are of this error  until we receive a request from HIMS department. \r\nSome one from IB needs to fix the error and send it to us so that the we can resolve the HIMs request','Ryan - This was re-assigned to Daniel Hom of the Bridges team.  The msgs erred in the IB (written to EHS logs) because the address field was too long (> 40 characters).  The only way to remediate the issue is to pick the msgs out of the Bridges outbound queue, truncate the address field value to 40 charaters and have an IB resource re-inject the msgs from the IB input queue on the Epic ADT to central process (MRMS) msg flow.\r\n\r\nDan - Ted Tablan reinjected the messages (A01 and A03) into the MRMS input queue.  They were received by Central Processing but were received in the reverse order so CP had to reinject the A03 message.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-02-14 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(160,1,NULL,6,NULL,'CA',NULL,'Hang filer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'INT','C','N',NULL,36,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,36,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(161,1,NULL,34,NULL,'GG',NULL,'EMPI CALLTIMED OUT',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-02 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'INT','C','N',NULL,36,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,36,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-02 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(162,1,NULL,36,NULL,'CA',NULL,'PYXIS ORDERS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-03 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'INT','C','N',NULL,36,9,'Epic didn\'t send out orders to Pyxis after Roseville Go live.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,36,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-03 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(163,1,NULL,34,NULL,'NB',NULL,'EMPI CALL TIMED OUT',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-04 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'INT','C','N',NULL,36,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,36,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2006-03-04 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,