omp, Commercial, COB, Self Pay, others TBD)\r\n2.	Clinical Care (PACTS, PHP, others TBD)\r\n3.	Division of Research (DOR)studies possibly interrupted \r\n4.	TPMG Statistics / CMIS utilization reports\r\n5.	eChart not showing 3/15 - 5/1 data, minimal impact','Epic provided a utility to identify all of the messages that went out incorrectly between 3/15 and 5/2 as well as a utility to retrigger the messages to Reg Plus/OSCR/CDR.  Remediation started 5/20/08 and finished 5/26/08 at 10:25 PM for the active encounter set of CPT4 codes.\r\n\r\nA total of 634,351 encounters were remediated (excluding the voids as described in item 3 below).\r\n\r\nEpic delivered the utility necessary to address the 894 voided CPT4 encounters late Friday, 6/6/08.  I will coordinate running the void utility on the shadow KPHC servers to determine exact counts, plan next steps, and determine final timeline for remediating production.  These are for encounters that occurred prior to 3/15 but had been voided during the 3/15 - 5/2 period.\r\n',30,30,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-06-17 10:04:00','2008-06-17 10:38:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(270,1,NULL,58,NULL,'CC',0,'Rad Transcription Filer Down',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'2008-06-26 00:00:00',NULL,'00:15',NULL,'INT','C',NULL,'L',37,NULL,'Rad Tx filer was down.... reason not known.','','','','','','','',37,37,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-06-27 10:19:00','2008-07-02 09:07:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(272,1,NULL,58,NULL,'AA',3539238,'Radiology - Messages finalize the report are not coming',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,'2008-06-26 00:00:00',NULL,'11 am',NULL,'MSG','C',NULL,'L',37,NULL,'Patients x-ray not transferring ovedr to KPHC.  Dr states that the x-ray has been interpreted has not crossed over.  X-ray was done on May 12.  Dr states that she can see it in cips but reads in process in kphc. \r\n\r\nKnown issue. \r\n\r\nBridges error:\r\n This message contains orders linked to multiple patient contacts\r\n\r\nDuplicate of ticket hd 3531555','Reassi